graph LR
    MLflow[MLflow Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    MLflow -->|cluster platform| K8s[Kubernetes v1.11.3+]
    MLflow -->|template engine| Helm[Helm v3 embedded]
    MLflow -->|deploys| MLflowImage[MLflow v3.6.0<br/>Container Image]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    MLflow -.->|TLS certs| ServiceCA[service-ca-operator<br/>OpenShift]
    MLflow -.->|metadata storage| PostgreSQL[PostgreSQL 9.6+]
    MLflow -.->|artifact storage| S3[S3-compatible Storage]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    MLflow -->|traffic routing| Gateway[data-science-gateway<br/>Gateway API HTTPRoute]
    MLflow -->|console integration| Console[OpenShift Console<br/>ConsoleLink CRD]
    MLflow -->|monitoring| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>ServiceMonitor]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH/RHOAI Dashboard] -.->|indirect access| MLflow
    Users[Data Scientists] -->|creates MLflow CRs| MLflow
    Users -->|accesses via| Gateway

    %% Build Dependencies (Build-time only)
    MLflow -.->|build-time| Go[Go v1.24.6+]

    %% API Server (Core dependency)
    MLflow -->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    K8sAPI -->|provides| RBAC[RBAC Enforcement]
    K8sAPI -->|provides| CRDs[CRD Management]

    %% Styling
    style MLflow fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px
    style K8s fill:#326ce5,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#326ce5,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Helm fill:#0f1689,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style MLflowImage fill:#0194e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    style ServiceCA fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style PostgreSQL fill:#336791,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style S3 fill:#f90,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px

    style Gateway fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Console fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Prometheus fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px

    style Go fill:#00add8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style RBAC fill:#d5e8d4,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style CRDs fill:#d5e8d4,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px

    %% Legend
    subgraph Legend[" "]
        direction TB
        L1["━━━ Required dependency"]
        L2["┄┄┄ Optional dependency"]
        L3["🔵 MLflow Operator (This component)"]
        L4["🔷 External Dependencies"]
        L5["🟢 Internal ODH/RHOAI"]
    end

